// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2314 — Mass File Rename (worldleaks)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 932ae052-12ab-5097-a9cf-dc488db190ca

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
